  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>船が出なかったせいで
守れなかった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Since the ship never set sail,
I wasn't able to protect it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おい、今度のは意味がわからないぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, this time we've got one I don't get at all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>確かにわからないな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't get him, either...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やめてあげて！
アスベルを責めるのは！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stop with that! It's not Asbel's fault!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>彼はちょっと運が悪いだけで
根は真面目ないい人なの！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He just has bad luck,
but he's an honest and wonderful person!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>俺は……今度こそ守ってみせる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I... will protect it this time!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なにをだ！！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Protect what?!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
